Basquiat Strings were nominated for the 2007 Mercury Prize.
The band performed an Electric Prom in 2008 featuring NY sax player Elery Eskerlin.
Ben moved to the Chicago USA in 2016 where he formed a trio with guitarist Sam Mosching and drummer Steve Hunt and a duo with guitarist Matt Gold.
